Clone an Enhanced Bot

Create a similar enhanced bot to quickly help with development, or grow your enhanced bot portfolio by creating similar bots for different use cases. You canâ€™t clone an enhanced bot as a standard bot.

To build and manage Einstein Bots:	
Customize Application OR
Modify Metadata OR
Manage Bots

Turn on Omni-Channel to allow Salesforce to create Omni-Channel flows to route conversations to and from your bot. Omni-Channel must be enabled to create and manage Omni-Channel flows.

Go to the Einstein Bot Setup page, find the enhanced bot you want to clone in the My Bots list, click the dropdown and select Clone.
Enter a unique bot display name and API name. Save your changes. The system clones the bot and enters the Bot Builder Dialogs page.

CONFIGURE ROUTING FOR YOUR BOT
INBOUND: SEND CONVERSATIONS TO YOUR ENHANCED BOT
OUTBOUND: TRANSFER CONVERSATIONS FROM YOUR ENHANCED BOT

When you clone an enhanced bot, inbound Omni-Channel flows don't automatically route conversations to your new bot. To route conversations to your new bot, visit Flow Builder and edit or create an inbound Omni-Channel flow from scratch.

The Outbound Omni-Channel Flow setting and associated outbound Omni-Channel flow are retained from the original bot and automatically transfer conversations from your new bot.

title: Clone an Enhanced Service Cloud Bot
